The server is implemented in Opa, cf. http://opalang.org
Compiling is:
opa server.opa
It creates a RESTful wiki server which supports the following methods: GET, POST, DELETE.
URL: http://server/_rest_/pagename?callback=callback
To get a list of pages:  http://server/_list_/?callback=callback
To get the global version number:  http://server/_version_/?callback=callback